df52da.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,12.231108940972,100,75.822222222222\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\"><em>Subnautica 2</em> was announced at Thursday\u2019s <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mF6rXas66ns&amp;rco=1\">Xbox Partner Preview</a>, and the follow-up to <em>Subnautica</em> will include an exciting new feature: co-op multiplayer for up to four players at once.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">In this new title, set to come out in 2025 through Xbox Game Preview, players will discover a new planet filled with challenges, creatures, and vehicles new and old. The multiplayer mode lets players dive into the unknown with their friends, but Xbox says the solo mode will be just as difficult and exciting as <em>Subn", "id": 1343599, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/news/466918/subnautica-2-announcement-multiplayer-new-planet", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Subnautica 2 will include multiplayer and take place on a new planet", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-17T12:41:16+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"A screenshot from Spycraft: The Great Game\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/Spycraft.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">If you watch one movie this year that features both former CIA director William Colby <em>and</em> Polygon co-founder Justin McElroy, make sure it&#8217;s <a href=\"https://youtu.be/tFYBsnVfT-w?feature=shared\">Polygon\u2019s documentary on <em>Spycraft: The Great Game</em></a>.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">A relic of the 1990s, <em>Spycraft: The Great Game</em> is an FMV point-and-click adventure that places you in the shoes of a CIA recruit thrust into a plot of international intrigue in the shadow of the Cold War. Activision spent millions of dollars on the development of <em>Spycraft</em>, which received critical acclaim upon i", "id": 1343161, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/what-to-buy/466800/spycraft-game-movie-where-to-buy", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Where you can play Spycraft, the game so wild we made a documentary about it", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-17T12:34:19+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"GTA Online promo art for Creepy Cat Masks\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Rockstar Games\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/GTA-Online-10172024-5.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p>The weekly <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/gta-online-guides\"><em><strong>GTA Online</strong></em></a><strong> update for October 17, 2024</strong>, is live with reward events, discounts, prizes, and slasher clones.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Our <em>GTA Online </em>weekly update guide will tell you everything happening in Los Santos this week.</p>\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\" />\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"tqxGpX\"><strong>GTA Onli