chests-locations-solutions-where-to-find", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Where to find all Gear Chest locations in Assassin\u2019s Creed Mirage", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-17T11:23:00+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Ubisoft Bordeaux/Ubisoft via Polygon\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24991920/ac_mirage_excavation_site.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p><strong>Finding the Excavation Site</strong> is central to the \u201cFind the Missing Brother\u201d quest in <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/game/assassins-creed-mirage/40915\"><em>Assassin\u2019s Creed Mirage</em></a>.</p>\n\n<p>Part of a larger quest arc in the Abbasiyah district, upon finishing your preliminary investigation in the House of Wisdom, you\u2019re told about a scholar that has disappeared, which means you\u2019ll have to look for him.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">This page explains where to <strong>find the Excavation Site location </strong>and discovering the clues that follow.</p>\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"", "id": 1342705, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/assassins-creed-mirage-guides/23909785/excavation-site-find-the-missing-brother", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0